
Release history for Importer-Zim

{{$NEXT}}

v0.9     2017-12-29 15:57:11-08:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Setup default backends with IMPORTER_ZIM_BACKEND
    - prereqs: Make +EndOfScope the fallback backend
    - dist.ini: use @Author::FERREIRA bundle

v0.8     2017-11-09 14:21:25-08:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - +Base gets loaded if import() gets called
    - From zim::import() to Import::Zim::Base::import_into()
    - export_to() function
    - Require +Base 0.12.0+
    - Require +Lexical 0.10.0+
    - Require +EndOfScope 0.4.0+
    - Require +Unit 0.5.0+
    - Require +Bogus 0.12.0+

v0.7     2017-11-02 09:29:51-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Require +Bogus 0.9.0+
    - Try +Bogus backend as last resort

v0.6     2017-09-29 14:44:56-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Produce DEBUG message with carp()
    - goto backend->import() to report from the correct location
    - Require Importer::Zim::Utils 0.8.0+
    - Require +Lexical 0.8.0+
    - Require +EndOfScope 0.2.0+
    - Require +Unit 0.3.0+

v0.5     2017-09-26 13:15:04-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Reduced perl requirement to 5.10.1
    - Try +Lexical, +EndOfScope, +Unit backends by default
    - Support to try alternative backends
    - Debugging enabled with IMPORTER_ZIM_DEBUG

v0.4     2017-09-22 10:51:00-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Handle "use IMPORTER MODULE => \@EXPORTS"
    - Require +Lexical 0.6.0+
    - Include a cookbook for usage examples

v0.3     2017-09-15 19:51:53-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Require +Lexical 0.5.0+

v0.2     2017-09-13 14:47:24-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Add SEE ALSO pod section
    - add DESCRIPTION pod section
    - Require +Lexical 0.4.0+

v0.1     2017-09-11 11:10:27-07:00 America/Los_Angeles

    - Support pluggable importer, like '+Lexical' or 'Importer::Zim::Lexical'
    - Require minimum version for Importer::Zim::Lexical

v0.0     2017-09-02

    - Initial commit
